ARC® Fertility & IVF Loans

 ARC® Fertility Financing: IVF Loans Make Treatment More Affordable

ARC makes it easy for you to afford care and quickly move forward.

You may finance any of the following:

  • Any ARC Fertility Treatment Package
  • Medical services you receive from your ARC physician
  • Fertility medications through the ARC Pharmacy Plan

IVF Loans and Payment Plans including 0% ZERO Interest

Sample Loan Amounts

Loan approvals up to $50,000. APRs start at and 3.99% for terms available up to 84 months, 0% zero-interest plans for 6 months.

IVF Loans and Payment Plans

ARC Fertility works with established and reputable lending partners who understand the unique needs of couples facing infertility. This helps make infertility treatment more affordable through extended payment programs and allows you to make manageable monthly payments.

Below is an example of how affordable IVF and other fertility treatments can be when financed with ARC:

ARC Loan Sample Amount

See the IVF Loan Chart below. $15,000 Loan terms starting at 3.99% APR for up to 84 months, with 0% zero-interest plans for 6 months also available.

ARC has resources for you to learn more about how you may improve your credit.

How to Apply

ARC Fertility Loans:

Contact an ARC Concierge Fertility Specialist by phone at 888-990-2727 or use the ARC Contact Form. They will provide you with an individualized quote for your selected Fertility Clinic and guide you through the financing process step-by-step.

Once you have an estimated quote for treatment at your Fertility Clinic, you can complete the fertility loan application using the button below.
